author: wn.com
title: US Blames Russia in Syria to Divert Attention From Kunduz Attack
text: Soon after the devastating attack on a hospital in the Afghani city of Kunduz, the US tried to lay the blame on the Afghani forces for providing wrong information and divert attention from the incident by criticizing Russia for its aerial campaign in Syria. ...
